WEBVTT

00:00:00.937 --> 00:00:02.633
Ovo je fotografija

00:00:02.633 --> 00:00:05.449
čovjeka čije sam ubojstvo

00:00:05.449 --> 00:00:07.310
godinama planirao.

00:00:09.170 --> 00:00:10.650
To je moj otac.

00:00:12.190 --> 00:00:15.927
Clinton George "Podočnjak" Grant.

00:00:15.927 --> 00:00:18.198
Zovu ga "Podočnjak" jer ima

00:00:18.198 --> 00:00:20.588
trajne vrećice ispod očiju.

00:00:22.358 --> 00:00:25.134
Kao desetogodišnjak,
s braćom i sestrama,

00:00:25.134 --> 00:00:29.250
maštao sam kako ću mu ubaciti

00:00:29.250 --> 00:00:31.840
otrov za muhe u kavu,